longBusinessSummary: Desert Gold Ventures Inc., an exploration stage company, engages in the acquisition, exploration, and development of mineral resource properties in Mali. The company primarily explores for gold ores. Its flagship project is the Senegal Mali Shear Zone project located in Western Mali. Desert Gold Ventures Inc. was incorporated in 2003 and is headquartered in Surrey, Canada.
